@startuml CoreNeedleBiopsy_Workflow_InfoRequest
title Szenario 7: Info-Anforderung\nCore Needle Biopsy – Fehlende klinische Angaben

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #AAAAAA
skinparam sequenceGroupFontSize 11
skinparam noteFontSize 10
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8DC

participant "**Placer (KIS)**\nUrologie" as Placer #BDD7EE
participant "**Filler (LIS)**\nPathologie" as Filler #C6EFCE

== Auftragserstellung (2024-01-15, 08:00) ==

Placer -> Filler : POST Bundle (type: **transaction**)\n  Patient\n  ServiceRequest (status: **active**)\n  Specimen [x12] (status: **available**)\n  Task (status: **requested**, code: fulfill)
activate Filler
Filler --> Placer : Bundle (type: **transaction-response**)\n  201 Created
deactivate Filler

note over Placer, Filler : **Task V1: requested**

== Eingangspruefung (2024-01-15, 14:00) ==

Filler -> Filler : Proben empfangen.\nKlinische Angaben pruefen:\n- PSA-Wert: **fehlt**\n- MRT/PI-RADS: **fehlt**\n- Vorbiopsie: **unklar**

== Info-Anforderung (2024-01-15, 14:30) ==

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task\n(status: **received**\nbusinessStatus: **"Awaiting Information"**)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

Filler -> Placer : POST Communication\n(about: Task\nstatus: in-progress\npayload: "Bitte nachreichen:\n1. Aktueller PSA-Wert\n2. MRT-Befund mit PI-RADS\n3. Vorbiopsie ja/nein + Ergebnis")
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 201 Created
deactivate Placer

note over Placer, Filler #FFFFCC : **Task V2: received**\nbusinessStatus: Awaiting Information\nWorkflow pausiert bis\nPlacer Informationen liefert

== Placer liefert Informationen (2024-01-16, 09:00) ==

Placer -> Filler : POST Observation (PSA)\n(code: LOINC 2857-1\nvalue: 8.5 ng/mL)
activate Filler
Filler --> Placer : 201 Created
deactivate Filler

Placer -> Filler : POST DocumentReference\n(type: MRT-Befund\ndescription: "PI-RADS 4,\nlaesionsverdaechtig rechts\napikal peripher")
activate Filler
Filler --> Placer : 201 Created
deactivate Filler

Placer -> Filler : POST Communication\n(about: Task\npayload: "PSA 8.5 ng/mL,\nPI-RADS 4 rechts apikal,\nkeine Vorbiopsie")
activate Filler
Filler --> Placer : 201 Created
deactivate Filler

== Workflow wird fortgesetzt (2024-01-16, 10:00) ==

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task\n(status: **accepted**)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

note over Placer, Filler : **Task V3: accepted**\nInformationen erhalten,\nAuftrag angenommen

== Bearbeitung (2024-01-16, 14:00) ==

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task\n(status: **in-progress**)

group Pathologische Aufarbeitung [3-5 Tage]
  Filler -> Filler : Makroskopie
  Filler -> Filler : Mikroskopie
  Filler -> Filler : Diagnostische Schlussfolgerung
end

== Befunderstellung & Abschluss (2024-01-20, 15:30) ==

Filler -> Placer : POST Bundle (type: **document**, signed)\n  Composition\n  DiagnosticReport (status: **final**)\n  Patient, ServiceRequest, Specimen\n  Observations
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 201 Created
deactivate Placer

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task\n(status: **completed**\noutput: Bundle)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

note over Placer, Filler : **Task V4: completed**

Placer -> Placer : ServiceRequest\n(status: **completed**)

note over Placer : Befund im KIS verfuegbar.\nKlinische Angaben im Befund\nberuecksichtigt (PSA, PI-RADS).

@enduml
